# Architecture Documents

This folder contains system design documentation.

## Suggested Documents

- `overview.md` - High-level system architecture
- `simulation.md` - Sim loop, physics, combat systems
- `environment.md` - Gym environment, observations, actions
- `training.md` - PPO pipeline, arena self-play
- `terrain.md` - World generation, biomes, validation
- `navigation.md` - Nav graph, planner, pathfinding

## Template

```markdown
# [Component] Architecture

## Overview
Brief description of this component's role.

## Components
- Component A: purpose
- Component B: purpose

## Data Flow
```
Input -> Processing -> Output
```

## Key Interfaces
- `function_name(args) -> return`: description

## Dependencies
- Internal: list modules
- External: list libraries

## Performance Considerations
Notes on hot paths, scaling, caching.
```
